Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稳着点  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steady, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,194)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵什么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is all that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is so funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopping hineys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put those away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少尴尬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be embarrassed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是你的宝宝照片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just your baby pictures
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那时真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was never adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些照片一个都不能留
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These photos have got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那时可真是个可爱的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were such a cute baby
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱到我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.96,0:01:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不可可爱爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not cute and adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可怕又邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm horrifying and evil
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板可是我见过最可爱的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton was the cutest baby I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要证明给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna prove it to him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也少让他遭罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keeps him off the streets
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该吃饭了  莫比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to eat, Moby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会爱上这款全新鲸鱼宝宝辅食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna love this new whale baby food
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名叫  鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called Baleen Baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了  莫比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Moby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.96,0:02:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜艇过来开进湖里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes the submarine into the lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Da-Da
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要我的鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my Baleen Baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,baby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他叫我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He called me Da-Da
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的孩子会边叫你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your kids will call you Da-Da
