Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get that for you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢  小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anytime, cutie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not a cutie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, what do I owe you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用钱的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on the house, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你实在很
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On account of you being so
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,famous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:05:01.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,144)}获胜者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:05:01.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1498,190)}鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.60,0:05:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭名远扬才对吧  不过也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pronounced "infamous," but okay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你今天愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我电视上看过那屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I seen that butt on the TV
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要我的鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my Baleen Baby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,baby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁股缝飞艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blimping butt cracks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy some Baleen Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,696)}来买鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,366)}鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,616)}鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1346,800)}鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.56,0:05:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你竟敢不经我允许传播我宝宝大头照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you give out my baby mugshots
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without my permission
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很想邀功  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As much as I'd like to, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这种事不能赖在我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take credit for this one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你一定高兴坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now aren't you happier knowing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟你还是全裤头村最可爱的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you're still the cutest baby in town?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要激发所有人心中的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to strike fear in the hearts of everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是要让老太婆捏我脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not make old ladies pinch my cheek
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我脸上的捏痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at these pinch marks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着就疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks painful
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻子才道歉  海绵笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry is for suckers, SpongeBoob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害得我因为宝宝照片搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me into this baby picture mess
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得帮我收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're gonna help me clean it up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(386,566)}鲸须宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1492,224)}获胜者
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,计划如下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the plan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我所有的宝宝照片都盖住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We cover up all my baby pictures
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是首先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要砍掉广告牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we chop down the billboards
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后往公交车广告撒油漆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, we paint over the bus ads
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,402)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And finally
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把鲸须宝贝辅食存货全买了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we buy up the entire supply of Baleen Baby food
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再埋到沙漠里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bury it in the desert
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.16,0:07:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.25,0:07:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也没谁会看我光身子的宝宝照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody will ever see my naked baby photos again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那那  那什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-what the heck was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海海  海郊狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-s-sea coyotes?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一群鲸鱼宝宝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a bunch of whale babies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们怎么那样子盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are they staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是闻到宝宝辅食味了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They probably smell the baby food
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说鲸鱼宝宝都吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do baby whales eat anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扔一罐过去  赶他们走得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toss 'em a jar and make 'em go away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  宝宝们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break it up, babies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break it up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲸须宝贝辅食成分为百分之百的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Baleen Baby food is made of 100%"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Gulp"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你咽什么口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck is "gulp"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,百分之百的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"100%
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮浮浮  浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,p-p-p-plankton"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,760)}配料\N{\fnArial}100%\N{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}浮游生物
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲸须宝贝就是浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baleen Baby is plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们都哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are they all coming from?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我还挺喜欢他们的鲸鱼歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I really dig their whale song
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不要听  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,据说鲸鱼宝宝的歌很有催眠效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some say the song of a baby whale is so hypnotic
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会把你同化成凶狠贪食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it can turn you into a voracious
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还爱吃浮游生物的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plankton-eating
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whale
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my mama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152,558)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(462,330)}A{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}级海霸糊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chum
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是打赌赌输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have lost a bet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a relief
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你们要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys were gonna eat--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝们  不要碰痞老板哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, babies, leave Plankton alone now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他们对我触须干了什么好事  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what they did to my antennas, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到哪都认得那屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd know that hiney anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是宝宝痞老板的明星屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are Baby Plankton's famous buns
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要来踹你屁股  怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll kick your buns, you weirdo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是要来给你鲸须宝贝比赛奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to give you the Baleen Baby contest check
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1558,514)}收款人 痞老板\N今天\N备注 可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共千千万万块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for one jillion dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,baby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这宝宝辅食的事就要另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a baby food of a different flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accept
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝痞老板味道像海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baby Plankton tastes like chum?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不太利于生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna be good for business
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  改变计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, change of plans
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再跟这位独眼博士合作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're done with Dr. Cyclops here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改用我们手上第二好的宝宝照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let's go with the second best baby photo we have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,372)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.87,0:11:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还把蟹老板的宝宝照片寄过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sent in Mr. Krabs' baby photo, too
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话  还挺可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好捏的脸蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pinchable cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.73,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFD3&}小海绵\N{\fs30} \N{\fs175}大灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:55.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(650,494)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(814,710)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.32,0:12:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才还在这边用功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Genius at work here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my golly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My painting
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我美丽的自画像成了一坨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You turned my beautiful self-portrait into a
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一坨海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a sponge-blob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it looks good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你懂什么  庶民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know, plebeian?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得把这玩意扔到它该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going where it belongs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾堆里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙儿过来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fellas, check this out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从未见过此般美丽的艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a profoundly beautiful work of art
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想起这混沌的世上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It reminds me that in this chaotic world
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依旧有着毫不掩饰之美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there is still unabashed beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都爱你的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People love your painting
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是收垃圾的  当然喜欢垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're garbage people, of course they like garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For your information
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们几个都有鲸鱼大学的艺术学位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we all got art degrees from Whale University
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点跳  我的小心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be still, my beating heart
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幅旷世巨作是谁画的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's responsible for this masterpiece?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.89,0:13:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是佩吉石斑海姆  头号画商
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Peggy Grouperheim, big-time art dealer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的画简直才华横溢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your painting is a work of sheer genius
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买下它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认可我的才华吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You recognize my genius?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you like that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定还会爱上我其他的画作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're gonna love my other paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不呢  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些玩意缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those lack the spark of
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幅画的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this painting
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.13,0:13:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个小鬼肯定就是你的灵感源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clearly, that little urchin is your muse
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我多画几幅画  专门画他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make me more paintings of him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候我会在我画廊里给你办特展
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll give you a show in my gallery
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我名片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my card
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她居然真喜欢你的画啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She actually liked your painting, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  她什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我专属的画廊特展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My own gallery show
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名声马上就能响彻全世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon, the whole world will know me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我出名的关键就是天分与艺术之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for my artistic soul, my genius
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我得画海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I gotta paint SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本就不想跟他共处同一片海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even like being in the same ocean with him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没办法叫他给我摆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't ask him to pose for me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.39,0:14:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接凭印象画他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just paint him from memory
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这么久都想忘掉海绵宝宝的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've spent so long trying to forget SpongeBob exists
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全忘了他长什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten what he looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩一个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing to do
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stealth painting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,440)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯条做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fries are ready
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做得不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those fries are off
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好把这滚烫的热油给换了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better change this boiling hot oil
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下班时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quittin' time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该去滑浪学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off to boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得来个更直接的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a more direct approach
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1120,654)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美术不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If fine arts aren't working
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就上武术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe martial arts will
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Them's my kids
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You-you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But-but
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.34,0:17:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来个更直接上不少的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for an even more direct approach
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've done it again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又画出了一幅美丽的旷世巨作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another beautiful masterpiece
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续与你的灵感源泉共事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep working with your muse
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你灵感源泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your muse?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let it go to your head
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你要我摆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you wanted me to pose, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接问我就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all you had to do was ask
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.55,0:18:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你实现艺术美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help you achieve your artistic dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You would?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来画画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's get painting
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要启发灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm musing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要启发灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm musing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要启发灵感  我要启发灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm musing, I'm musing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站到那上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand up there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.48,0:18:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只手放你臀部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, put one hand on your hip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一只举到半空中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and raise the other in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得这姿势行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think about this pose?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选好姿势不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just pick a pose and stay still
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.79,0:18:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说了不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said stay still
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.73,0:18:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没咋捕捉到我成熟又天真的品质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't quite captured
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my quality of mature naivete
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该当我灵感源泉  不是批评我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be my muse, not my critic
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我能画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can paint
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能往前挪一点点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you scoot forward?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the chair
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  麻烦不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, please stay still
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁放屁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody step on a duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(958,920)}踩 鸭 子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.03,0:21:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来章鱼哥不觉得我好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess Squidward didn't find me amusing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:09.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1256,920)}启发灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(924,260)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The way out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来画灵感源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paint the muse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来画灵感源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paint the muse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来画我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paint me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远永远永远画一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever and ever and ever
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就画你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll paint you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就画死你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll paint you to oblivion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go a-painting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画画了  画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-painting, a-painting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go a-painting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天浑浑噩噩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the ding-dong day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来让章鱼哥发大财
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to make Squidward rich
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便让我发更大的财
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and me richer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我又把一位艺术家逼得太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I pushed another artist too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给他的旧画抬价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mark up the prices of his old paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我名气尽失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may have lost all my fame
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金钱也尽失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and money
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.36,0:22:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过起码  我又喜欢上画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but at least, I enjoy painting again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你画完了没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, you finished with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.41,0:22:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.67,0:22:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
